==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Intraparietal
<hw>In"tra*pa*ri"e*tal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Situated or
occurring within an inclosure; shut off from public sight; private;
secluded; retired.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I have no Turkish proclivities, and I do not think that, after
all, impaling is preferable as a mode of capital punishment to
<qex>intraparietal</qex> hanging.</q> <rj><qau>Rolleston.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Intrapetiolar</ent>⟦br⟧
